text: Alone/Together is a 2019 Filipino romantic drama movie directed by Antoinette Jadaone and starring Enrique Gil, Liza Soberano, Jasmine Curtis-Smith, Sylvia Sanchez, Adrian Alandy. It was distributed by ABS-CBN Films. ==Other websites== * Category:2019 romantic drama movies Category:Filipino movies Category:Movies directed by Antoinette Jadaone
